"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*cw9HabJywGpmWNxHnsi3TA.png)\\n\\n## WIP32 Review\\n\\nIn this proposal, the core development team proposes a specific plan for WePiggy to be deployed on the Harmony mainnet, and makes appropriate explanations to the relevant content to clarify the specific reasons and motivations as much as possible.\\n\\n**Option:**\\n\\nOption 1: For this planOption 2: Against this plan\\n\\nThe core development team will implement this proposal according to the option with the most votes in this voting.\\n\\nFor more details, check here: <https://gov.wepiggy.com/t/topic/1156>\\n\\n## Formal Voting\\n\\nNow, community members can vote through the formal voting website: [https://vote.wepiggy.com](https://vote.wepiggy.com/).\\n\\n**Voting Network:** Please switch to **Ethereum Mainnet** to vote\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*Time：\\\\*\\\\*2021/12/26 10:00–2021/12/28 10:00 (UTC+8 Time)\\n\\n**Voting group:** WPC holders on Ethereum, OKExChain, BSC, Polygon, HECO, Arbitrum, Optimism and Moonriver mainnet.\\n\\n**Voting power calculation:**\\n\\nThe system will take snapshots of all user addresses at 0:00 every day, and calculate the total amount of WPC held by each user on all chains.\\n\\nThe voting power of each user in this voting is based on the snapshot taken at 0:00 on the voting day, one WPC one vote.\\n\\n## Tutorial of voting：\\n\\n[https://www.yuque.com/zgryhn/duu5f7/uzfhic](https://www.yuque.com/zgryhn/duu5f7/uzfhic)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640762818,\"title\":\"WIP32 Formal Voting Begins!\"},\"digest\":\"lrx2szFu-amsQ23SQlXzoxztTXo_lq2TfU8YbiY5cdM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"03yhYBnjqelR9H8Ovo5QPUHwy_GUUGmdM8Qrq2aYDMc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"tykyJY8I4SRjXAG9rNOUB9kKRqXuX2zXaajgf6IStAA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"tr40Z3v4SgGelUNJBIwC9h65Zy5KWh69-HsIWs4